    slug: "asmad-surma-large",
    description: `Asmad Surma in the large size is a traditional Islamic eye cosmetic product that follows the prophetic practice of applying kohl (surma) to the eyes. The use of surma is deeply rooted in Islamic tradition, with numerous hadith narrations attributing the practice to Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him), who recommended it for its perceived benefits to eye health and vision. The word "Asmad" refers to the quality of the kohl, and this large-sized container provides a generous quantity of finely milled, dark powdered kohl that can be applied to the inner rim of the eyelids using a traditional surma applicator or a thin wand. The product is formulated from natural mineral-based ingredients, primarily derived from antimony sulfide or galena, which have been used for centuries across the Muslim world and the broader Middle Eastern and South Asian regions as a natural eye cosmetic.

The physical packaging of this large Asmad Surma comes in a durable container that keeps the powder secure and prevents spillage during everyday use and travel. The compact yet substantial design of the large size ensures that the product lasts for an extended period, making it a practical choice for regular users who apply surma as part of their daily grooming routine following the sunnah. The dark powder delivers a rich, intense color that defines the eyes naturally and provides a traditional appearance that has been favored in Muslim cultures for generations. The texture of the kohl is finely ground to ensure smooth application without irritation, and the formulation is intended to be gentle enough for regular use on the sensitive skin around the eyes.

Applying surma has been a consistent practice among Muslim men and women for over fourteen centuries, and this product continues that tradition in a convenient, ready-to-use format. The large size is particularly suitable for families where multiple members use surma regularly, or for individuals who prefer to keep a substantial supply on hand. The container is designed to be portable, allowing users to carry it in a bag or pocket for reapplication throughout the day. In many Muslim households, surma is one of the essential personal care items maintained at all times, and this large Asmad Surma provides a reliable supply of this traditional product that connects contemporary users to the sunnah practices of the Prophet Muhammad (peace be upon him). The product is also commonly given as a gift during Ramadan, Eid, and other special occasions, reflecting its cultural significance as both a cosmetic item and a religiously meaningful practice.`,
    metaDescription: "Asmad Surma in large size is a traditional natural kohl following the prophetic sunnah. Fine dark powder in a durable container for regular eye care use."
